    "Additionally, LLMs are employed in the internal processes of the newly implemented service name generation API and keyword extraction API.",
    "All of these LLMs are based on gpt -3.5- turbo.",
    "To prevent undesired outcomes from being generated, the sampling temperature was set to 0.0.",
    "For both the service name generation API and the keyword extraction API, two input-output examples were provided using few-shot prompting before executing the prompts.In this study, three APIs were implemented to integrate our prior interactive need extraction system with the SUC-CEED system, forming a unified process for obtaining development information.",
    "APIs allow external programs to invoke specific processes, and by implementing them, the proposed method can be integrated across various systems."
